line-format-adapter --- Internal Programming Utility
====================================================

Description
-----------
Simplifies the development of modules which modify the textual contents of
lines in LineEditors and the BufferEditor, such as replacing control characters
with textual representations.

Configuration
-------------
None.

Weight (always active)
----------------------
Two hook invocations every time a BufferEditor line is to be prettified, or a
LineEditor's contents to be displayed.
